This is my first trial to communicate between iPhone and Max/MSP.\
In this time, you can only send any text from iPhone to Max/MSP when you tap a button on iPhone. I think you can't implement a mousedown and mousemove behavior due to the limitation of iPhone OS/UI.\
\
\

