\f0\b [ Usage ]
\f1\b0 \
\
(1) Open "aka.iphone1.pat" with Max/MSP.\
\
(2) Open "http://your-computer-ip-address/~your-usename/test1/" with Safari on iPhone.\
\
(3) Tap any button on the web page of iPhone. You will see a message on Max/MSP.\
